4) Use AWS Identity and Access Management roles for EC2 instances.(securely passing credentials)

5)Source/Destination check should be disabled on NAT Instance.

6)Amazon Elastic Block Store (Amazon EBS) sends data points to CloudWatch for several metrics.
All Amazon EBS volume types automatically send 1-minute metrics to CloudWatch, but only when the volume is attached to an instance.

